AUDIO: '&gt;&gt; The lip sync is not bad. It\'s not only able to animate his face, but his entire body, including hand gestures to kind of match the context and the dialogue. Now, you can also specify different actions within the scene and specify which'

[01:05] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'character talks. So, for example, here we have a uniformed woman in the foreground taking a step forward, her gaze remaining fixed on the young woman, then she speaks, "Come here.'

[01:17] [scene:talk]
