[01:31] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'hand is slightly raised. She opens her eyes looking down into the left, etc., etc. And then she continues, "Is that?" And then we can expand the prompt to guide her expression and actions further. And then she continues saying,'

